Ref Sanchez https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ref_Sanchez 0 Ref Sanchez (born Refugio Sanchez in Arizona, 1917; died 1986) was an American actor who appeared mostly in television shows in smaller acting parts. He worked as a fashion photographer in the 1950s through the 1970s.
